				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: With GoD AA's...our Best Weapon DPS Combo?<a name="31541"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Mar 30 04 2:25 AM</span></td>
