This was going based on Weapon Affinity 5, and at least +10 to combat Effects....while Main-handing the ED.  Of course everyone at this point is 305 Dex.
<br />

<br />
The 1.8 a minute is just base.  If you're doing more than Base, you're getting a more dramatic difference between the ED and the EoE's procs.  For this I was using a 2.8.
<br />

<br />
This also doesn't take into account Spell Casting Fury 3, which adds about 7% damage to the procs.
<br />

<br />
Like I said, I'm talking about Main-hand weapon here....not Off-hand.  Songblade would be Off-handed...it has a better ratio yes, but it has no proc whatsoever.(The Effect is Right-click).
<br />

<br />
I dunno who's tanking even with Time gear but it's certainly not me, heh, as Harm said we still can't hold agro.  This isn't a tanking Combo though it's just aiming for DPS.  The only time I tank is duel-boxing with my cleric solo -- although I do that a fair amount, I hold just barely enough agro to out-do CH's.
<br />

<br />

<br />
And again I realize DPS is not our main focus.  But sometimes when I'm farming greens or something I want pure DPS.</span></td>
